      "para_id": "Q001049.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(iv 1) Šul-MUŠxPA , the personal god of the king , carried the pure earth-basket ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001049.5",
      "line_range": "5",
      "translation": "(iv 5) Ur-Nanše , king of Lagaš , child of Gunidu , citizen of Gursar , built the shrine of Ĝirsu ."
    }
